Subject: [PATCH 3/3] PR A3: replace mat_plot_2d.plot_array in
 FitImagingMeta with plot_array()

Bridge FitImagingMeta.figures_2d() to use the new direct-matplotlib
plot_array() function via a _plot_array() helper method, eliminating the
MatWrap system for fit imaging plots.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01CzJBy8KvFXiNchoNdk5i9k
